                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The two-headed goat gains an extra reaction each round that it can use only to make Attacks of Opportunity. It must use a different head for each reaction, and it can't use more than one on the same triggering action. If it loses one of its heads, it also loses this extra reaction.</p>"
                },
