        {
            "_id": "ieFGm768pfF5Hpwe",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Two Headed",
            "sort": 600000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Any ability that would sever one of the twoheaded goat's heads (such as a critical hit with a vorpal weapon) severs one head at random. Losing a head doesn't kill the two-headed goat (as long as it has one head left), but it does prevent it from making Strikes with the lost head or using the head's Breath Weapon.</p>"
                },
